===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues <https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues>`_.

`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_it_pec%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.
